Unless you make it many small shell aliases, such as these:<p><pre><code>    urlescape () { perl -MURI::Escape -lne &#x27;print uri_escape($_)&#x27; <<< &quot;$1&quot;; }
    urlunescape () { perl -MURI::Escape -lne &#x27;print uri_unescape($_)&#x27; <<< &quot;$1&quot;; }
</code></pre>
Then you can reuse them often. :)
